(75, 1, '2013-12-05 04:16:31', '2013-12-05 04:16:31', '<p>At Elliot James, we bring the finest elements of British interior design to Singapore; combining the unique heritage of England with the fashions and trends of London, set against the clean lines of this cutting edge city creating a truly bespoke interior solution that will harmoniously merge with your personality and tastes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Elliot James we are meticulous in our craft. We manage every second of the project and inspect every inch of the interior; after all, quality lies within the detail. For us, the finish must be perfect, edges must align and lines must be sharp. British interior designers are reowned for such attention to detail and Elliot James is no exceptation. At Elliot James we provide that British standard of design and build revered throughout the world to Singapore, creating luxury, opulence and style, regardless of budget.</p>\r\n', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2013-12-23 08:56:42', '2013-12-23 08:56:42', '', 0, 'http://www.http://localhost/EliotJames/?p=75', 0, 'post', '', 0),
